targets.rawSql:
SELECT
   CAST(result->>'throughput' AS DOUBLE PRECISION) AS "throughput"
FROM test_table
WHERE
   $__timeFilter("time") AND
   benchmark_type = 'tatp' AND
   terminals = '16'

SELECT
   MAX(CAST(result->>'throughput' AS DOUBLE PRECISION)) AS "throughput"
FROM test_table
WHERE
   $__timeFilter("time") AND
   benchmark_type = 'tatp' AND
   terminals = '16'
GROUP BY terminals
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
   AVG(CAST(result->>'throughput' AS DOUBLE PRECISION)) AS "throughput"
FROM test_table
WHERE
   $__timeFilter("time") AND
   benchmark_type = 'tatp' AND
   terminals = '16'
GROUP BY terminals
ORDER BY 1

   min(CAST(result->>'throughput' AS DOUBLE PRECISION)) AS "throughput"

ORDER BY 1
